text: Susan M. Tracy (born August 24, 1960 in Boston, Massachusetts) is an American political consultant and politician who represented the 19th Suffolk District in the Massachusetts House of Representatives from 1991 to 1995. She was a candidate in the 1998 Massachusetts 8th congressional district race. She finished eight out of ten candidates in the Democratic primary. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Politicians from Boston Category:Boston College alumni Category:John F.
